{
  "stem": "15694.12",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's why I calculated the amount of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were dying by the hour, more and more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And in-between, there was a walkway between one side and the other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that's where the soup was put.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I had, where the table was next to mine, a little bit of a bigger gap because there was a window between me and the next bed on this side.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went, I took the blanket, and I walked past the container with hot watery soup-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and with the idea of-- if they can live on a little bit of watery soup, if I get a couple of spoons more, I will survive better.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say now that it is-- was more the spirit than anything else that helped me survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I made a few passes near this container.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the third or fourth time, with a blanket on my right side sort of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] over it, I bent down and open the container.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Next, I went to my bed, took my soup-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] soup disk?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What is soup-- Dish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dish-- soup dish, metal soup dish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while I was passing again, lifted it, and scooped, you know, some soup out of it, very hot, scalding my thumb.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But who cares?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I thought because of the blanket on top that nobody had seen it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And slowly, I made my way to the nearby bed, took out-- took my spoon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I couldn't eat before everybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I bent down on my knees and wondered-- with the head under the bed, intended to eat my soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in no time, I was surrounded by a herd of growling wolves.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
